ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2009-10
PrecisAppointment of RUTH ARCHIBALD as High Commissioner for Canada to Antigua and Barbuda, the Federation of St. Kitts and Nevis, with residence in Bridgetown; ADÈLE DION as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Namibia, with residence in Pretoria; CAROLINE CHRÉTIEN as High Commissioner for Canada to Tuvalu, with residence in Wellington; JEAN-CAROL PELLETIER as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Sao Tomé and Principe, with residence in Yaounde; and CHRISTOPHER WILKIE as Ambassador of Canada to the Islamic Republic of Mauritania, with residence in Rabat.
